This repository is the in-progress development of 4neverCompany OS, a
packaged-desktop integration of Paperclip, Hermes Agent, and the BMAD
Method. The project has NOT been officially released. No version 1.0,
beta, or general-availability product has been published.

The source code and documentation in this repository are made publicly
visible for transparency, technical commentary, and to invite issue
reports — NOT to grant a redistribution or modification license.

WHAT YOU MAY DO
---------------

  * Read the source code, documentation, and commit history.
  * Fork this repository on GitHub (per GitHub's Terms of Service).
  * Open issues, discussions, and pull requests against this repository.
  * Build and run the project locally for evaluation purposes only.
  * Quote short excerpts in commentary, reviews, or research with
    attribution.

WHAT YOU MAY NOT DO (until a final license is published)
--------------------------------------------------------

  * Redistribute the source code or compiled binaries — in whole or in
