    repository.
  * Deploy this software in any production, customer-facing, or
    commercial environment.
  * Create derivative products or competing distributions based on this
    codebase.
  * Use the "4never", "Code4Never", "4neverCompany OS", or related
    project names, logos, or visual identity for any marketing,
    branding, or product naming.

